This is a Portfolio web app created using following technologies on cloud9.
Technologies used 
•	Node.js 
•	Express
        o	express-messages
        o	session
        o	connect-flash and 
        o	validation
•	MongoDB
•	Mongoose
•	Pug template engine
•	Passport.js authentication
•	Bcrypt hashing and 
•	Nodemailer
 
To know more about the project, please check the project report in source "project 619 axb6412"

node version- v8.9.1

Installation

1)Install the dependencies
$ npm install ... --save

2)Connect to MongodB
$ ./mongod

3)Start the server
$ npmstart

4)Run the application app.js